data.description: Welcome to your dream home with a layout perfectly designed for your comfort and convenience.  The floorplan, with three bedrooms down (including the primary) and one HUGE bedroom upstairs, could EASILY be three bedrooms down plus an office or additional living space upstairs (there's a full bathroom upstairs).  Or, you could even use the four bedrooms and have the media room upstairs for movie watching or even a home gym.  Your options are endless! The dedicated office downstairs is perfect for remote work or creative pursuits. This home is situated at the back of a small, quiet neighborhood, overlooking a peaceful field for additional privacy. The neighborhood park is one street away. Come see this home today and imagine all the ways you can make it your own.
